  "heading": "History",
  "bodyHtml": "\n\t<div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align:center;\"><strong><font size=\"4\"><font color=\"#8d2424\">Encouraging, developing, promoting, and preserving fiddle music as part of our culture and heritage.</font><br>​</font></strong></div>\n\n<h2 class=\"wsite-content-title\" style=\"text-align:left;\">History</h2>\n<div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align:left;display:block;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(121, 121, 121); font-weight:400\"><span style=\"color:rgb(121, 121, 121); font-weight:400\">Until 1999, Manitoba was the only Canadian province that did not have a Fiddle Association. But, on February 6th, 1999, a group of around 40 fiddlers from across Manitoba attended a meeting and elected an executive council for the Manitoba Fiddle Association (MFA). On March 9th, 1999, the MFA was officially incorporated as a non-profit corporation under The Manitoba Corporations Act.</span></span></div>\n\n<h2 class=\"wsite-content-title\" style=\"text-align:left;\">Executive</h2>\n<div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align:left;display:block;\"><span style=\"color:rgb(121, 121, 121); font-weight:400\"><span style=\"color:rgb(121, 121, 121); font-weight:400\"><span style=\"color:rgb(121, 121, 121); font-weight:400\"><span style=\"color:rgb(121, 121, 121); font-weight:400\"><span style=\"color:rgb(121, 121, 121); font-weight:400\"><span style=\"color:rgb(121, 121, 121); font-weight:400\">President&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></span></span><strong>Lyla Bilton</strong>, Winnipeg<br><span style=\"color:rgb(121, 121, 121); font-weight:400\"><span style=\"color:rgb(121, 121, 121); font-weight:400\"><span style=\"color:rgb(121, 121, 121); font-weight:400\"><span style=\"color:rgb(121, 121, 121); font-weight:400\"><span style=\"color:rgb(121, 121, 121); font-weight:400\"><span style=\"color:rgb(121, 121, 121); font-weight:400\">Past President&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></span></span><strong>Reg Delannoy</strong>, Winnipeg<br><span style=\"color:rgb(121, 121, 121); font-weight:400\"><span style=\"color:rgb(121, 121, 121); font-weight:400\"><span style=\"color:rgb(121, 121, 121); font-weight:400\"><span style=\"color:rgb(121, 121, 121); font-weight:400\"><span style=\"color:rgb(121, 121, 121); font-weight:400\"><span style=\"color:rgb(121, 121, 121); font-weight:400\">Vice President&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></span></span>Open<br><span style=\"color:rgb(121, 121, 121); font-weight:400\"><span style=\"color:rgb(121, 121, 121); font-weight:400\"><span><span><span><span><span>Treasurer&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></span></span><strong><span style=\"color:#797979\">Pat Thomas-Kuhl</span></strong>, Por<span style=\"color:rgb(121, 121, 121); font-weight:400\"><span style=\"color:rgb(121, 121, 121); font-weight:400\"><span style=\"color:rgb(121, 121, 121); font-weight:400\"><span style=\"color:rgb(121, 121, 121); font-weight:400\">tage la Prairie<br>Secretary&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;</span></span></span></span></span></span>​Open</div>\n\n<h2 class=\"wsite-content-title\" style=\"text-align:left;\">Directors</h2>\n<div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align:left;display:block;\"><strong>Gail Beam</strong>,&nbsp;Portage la Prairie<br><strong>Brian Granger</strong>, Nesbitt<br><strong>Basil McCallister</strong>,&nbsp;Portage la Prairie<br>​<strong>Roland Rey</strong>, St. Claude<br><strong>Heather Sharp</strong>, Portage la Prairie</div>\n\n<h2 class=\"wsite-content-title\" style=\"text-align:left;\">Area Representatives<br></h2>\n<div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align:left;display:block;\"><strong>Mike Armstrong</strong>, The Pas<br>​​<strong>Brian Granger</strong>, Nesbitt<br><strong>Boris Nowasad</strong>, Dauphin</div>\n\n<h2 class=\"wsite-content-title\" style=\"text-align:left;\"><span style=\"text-decoration:none; font-style:normal; font-weight:400; color:rgb(179, 60, 60); \"><span style=\"text-decoration:none; font-style:normal; font-weight:400; color:rgb(179, 60, 60); \">Newsletter Editor<br></span></span></h2>\n<div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align:left;display:block;\"><strong>Michelle Sorin</strong>, Lorette<br>​Please see the <a href=\"/contact.html\">Contact</a> section for newsletter submissions.</div>\n\n<h2 class=\"wsite-content-title\" style=\"text-align:left;\">Membership<br>       </h2>\n\n<div class=\"paragraph\" style=\"text-align:left;\">Please see the <a href=\"/join.html\">Join</a>&nbsp;section for membership information.</div>\n",
